html
  body
    .page-header
      h1
    .panel.panel-default
      .panel-heading Active Devices
      .panel-body
        p
          | Active devices are devices that are fully working as daily drivers, it requires to have wifi, call, sms, data, OTA, apparmor and sound to be working to be an &quot;Active device&quot;.
      table.table.table-hover
        thead
          tr
            th Priority
            th Name
            th Device
            th Comment
            th(style='width: 3%;')
        tr(ng-if='loading', align='center')
          th(colspan='5', style='text-align: center;')
            span.fa.fa-refresh.fa-spin.fa-3x
        tr(ng-if='hasActiveDev', ng-repeat='item in activeDevices', ng-click='go(item.device)')
          td {{item.pri}}
          td {{item.name}}
          td {{item.device}}
          td(style='width: 45%')
            | {{item.comment}}
          td
            span.fa.fa-chevron-right.pull-right
        tr(ng-if='!hasActiveDev && !loading', align='center')
          th(colspan='5', style='text-align: center;') Sorry, there is no &quot;Active&quot; devices yet!
    br
    .panel.panel-default
      .panel-heading Inprogress Devices
      .panel-body
        | Inprogress devices are devices that are not yet ready to use daily, due to missing important functions. These devices are under heavy development.
      table.table.table-hover
        thead
          tr
            th Priority
            th Name
            th Device
            th Devopment done
            th(style='width: 3%;')
        tr(ng-if='loading', align='center')
          th(colspan='5', style='text-align: center;')
            span.fa.fa-refresh.fa-spin.fa-3x
        tr(ng-repeat='item in progressDevices', ng-click='go(item.device)')
          td {{item.pri}}
          td {{item.name}}
          td {{item.device}}
          td(style='width: 45%')
            .progress
              .progress-bar(role='progressbar', aria-valuenow='{{item.done}}', aria-valuemin='0', aria-valuemax='100', style='width: {{item.done}}%; color: black;') {{item.done}}%
          td
            span.fa.fa-chevron-right.pull-right
    br
    .panel.panel-default
      .panel-heading Voting Devices
      .panel-body
        | Voting device are devices that haven&apos;t started development, users can vote (donate) for devices they want to get ported. A device will need to be bought so we can develop on it. Priority will be ranked after donate to debug device percentage.
      table.table.table-hover
        thead
          tr
            th Priority
            th Name
            th Device
            th Donations to Debug device
            th(style='width: 3%;')
        tr(ng-if='loading', align='center')
          th(colspan='5', style='text-align: center;')
            span.fa.fa-refresh.fa-spin.fa-3x
        tr(ng-repeat='item in voteDevices', ng-click='go(item.device)')
          td {{item.pri}}
          td {{item.name}}
          td {{item.device}}
          td(style='width: 45%')
            .progress
              .progress-bar(role='progressbar', aria-valuenow='{{item.donates}}', aria-valuemin='0', aria-valuemax='{{item.price}}', style='width: {{item.donates/item.price*100}}%; color: black;') {{item.donates/item.price*100}}%
          td
            span.fa.fa-chevron-right.pull-right
